@@TJvExBitBtn
Summary
  Base class for extended bitmap buttons.
Description
  TJvExBitBtn is a base class for classes in the JVCL library that descend from TBitBtn.

  Do not create instances of TJvExBitBtn. The TJvBitBtn class provides a generic implementation
  of TJvExBitBtn. You can also create your own descendant class.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
